NOTE:
the kernel is the same as the v3 stable images.
all entries in changelog are related to root_chooser since it's the only difference from v3.

ChangeLog:
using console for printing messages.
using /data/.root.d/ as configuration directory
using /data/.root as default configuration
removed support for temporary boot file
remove support for /root_chooser.log logfile
added user input handing
added menu printing
added timeout on choosing entry
now we pause on errors.
BUGFIX: call fflush before forking. ( or you see two <ENTER> query )
